graph TD

    %% Tiers definition

    subgraph Client_Tier [Client Tier]

        App[React Native / Expo Mobile App]

    end

    subgraph Backend_Tier [Backend / Logic Tier - Firebase]

        Auth[Firebase Authentication]

        Functions[Cloud Functions]

        FCM[Firebase Cloud Messaging]

    end



    subgraph Data_Tier [Data Tier]

        Firestore[(Cloud Firestore - Real-time DB)]

        Storage[(Firebase Storage - Media)]

    end



    %% Communication Flow

    App -->|1. Authenticate| Auth

    App <-->|2. Real-time Sync / Report Submission| Firestore

    App -->|3. Upload Evidence Photo/Video| Storage

    App -->|4. Trigger SOS Alert| Firestore




    %% Logic & Notifications

    Firestore -->|6. Trigger on Status Change| Functions

    Functions -->|7. Send Push Notification| FCM

    FCM -->|8. Alert Nearby Users| App



    %% Styling for better presentation

    style Client_Tier fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style Backend_Tier fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style Data_Tier fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style Firestore fill:#fff

    style Storage fill:#fff
